<div class="container">
   <h2 class="smallheadings">About Us</h2>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
            <p align="justify" class="aboutus">
                Welcome to City of Cincy – Your Gateway to a Rewarding Career in the Public Sector!

                At City of Cincy, we are committed to bridging the gap between talented individuals and meaningful public sector careers. 
                Our platform is dedicated to serving the public interest by connecting job seekers with opportunities in government, education, healthcare, and other essential public sector fields.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <img width="400x" src="~/Images/Homescreenimage2.png" />
        </div>
    </div>
