    <h2 class="smallheadings">Our Mission and Values</h2>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
            <p align="justify" class="aboutus">
                Empowering Public Service Careers: Our mission is to empower individuals who are passionate 
                about public service to find the perfect opportunities 
                to make a positive impact on their communities, cities, and countries.
                <br />
             <ul align="justify" class="aboutus">
                <li>Integrity: We uphold the highest standards of ethics and transparency in all our interactions.</li>
                <li>Public Service Commitment: We share a genuine commitment to the principles of public service and civic responsibility.</li>
                <li>Inclusivity: We celebrate diversity and believe in creating a platform where opportunities are accessible to all.</li>
                <li>Innovation: We constantly innovate and improve our services to meet the evolving needs of the public sector job market.</li>
            </ul>
            </p>

